2. In this Act-                                                    Interpreta-
                                                                     tion.
“the Board” means the Board of Directors of the Brother-
    hood, to be established in accordance with this Act;
“the Brotherhood” means the Port Royal Brotherhood to
    be established in accordance with this Act;
“the Chairman” means the Chairman of the Brotherhood
    and includes any person appointed in accordance with
    subsection (2) of section 5 to act as Chairman;
“the Committee” means the Assessment Committee to be
    constituted under subsection (1) of section 16;
“the relevant area” has the meaning assigned to it by sub-
    section (1) of section 15;
“the Secretary” means the Secretary of the Brotherhood.
       Establishment and Constitution ofBrotherhood
